<h1>Blueberry Muffins</h1>

<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Traditional blueberry muffins for Christmas eating</p>

<h2>Ingredients</h2>

<ul>
<li>2T Shortening</li>
<li>2C Flour</li>
<li>2&1/2t Baking Powder</li>
<li>1t Salt</li>
<li>1/4C Sugar</li>
<li>1 or 2 eggs</li>
<li>1C Milk</li>
<li>1C Blueberries or 3/4C Canned</li>
</ul>

<h2>Instructions</h2>

<ul>
<li>Add berry juice to milk mixture for extra flavor</li>
<li>Bake 425 for 28 min </li>
</ul>
